  "title": "Security Officer X 5 (Island Wide / Training Provided)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>Permanent full-time role</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Basic $2870 to $3600 + Allowances + JOINING BONUS</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Training Provided</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Responding to incidents and managing security and safety systems.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Preventing unauthorized entry into premises.</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Monitoring CCTV for suspicious activity.</strong></li>\n  <li>Conducting patrols and clocking duties.</li>\n  <li>Performing access control duties.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Able to commit 12 hours duty (Permanent day and/or night shift available)</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now button</strong> with the following information in the resume</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li>\n  <li>Current and Expected salary</li>\n  <li>Reason for leaving</li>\n  <li>Date of availability</li>\n  <li>Education background</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>LIONG ZHAO GUAN (R22107632)</p>\n<p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
